title: Paul Ryan: Russia Didn't Tell Hillary Clinton Not To Go To Wisconsin Or Michigan
text:
Paul Ryan: Russia Didn't Tell Hillary Clinton Not To Go To Wisconsin Or Michigan | Posted By Ian Schwartz   . @SpeakerRyan on election and #russianhack : "Russian didn't tell @HillaryClinton not to go to Wisconsin or Michigan." pic.twitter.com/yRx1pzmrsg 
Speaker of the House Paul Ryan talks about Russia interference in U.S. elections. Ryan said while Russia "clearly tried to meddle" in the presidential election, the nation did not force Hillary Clinton not to campaign in Wisconsin or Michigan. "He won the election fair and square, clearly and convincingly," Ryan said of Trump. . @SpeakerRyan "Russia clearly tried to meddle in our political system." #russianhack pic.twitter.com/TZEErvBbeS
